 Affzo NCSPLANNER(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_NCSPLANNER(zc) From W1NCSH2
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_NCSPLANNER(zc) From W1NCSH2
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_NCSPLANNER(zc) From W1NCSH2
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_NCSPLANNER(zc) From W1NCSH2
